OL,5, The BBC should have "thoroughly        
OL,6, investigated" after managers were told 
OL,7, Russell Brand had exposed himself to a 
OL,8, woman in a BBC office in 2008,         
OL,9, broadcast union Bectu has said.        
OL,11,FBBC News management were told in 2019  
OL,12,Fby a staff member about Brand's alleged
OL,13,Fbehaviour in the BBC News Los Angeles  
OL,14,Foffice. No formal action was taken.    
OL,16,FBrand was recording his Radio 2 show,  
OL,17,Fin which he laughed about the incident.
OL,19,FThe BBC said it would investigate the  
OL,20,Fallegations.                           
